OL,3,COfficer 'did not act with sensitivity'
OL,4,Cat Sean Graham memorial
OL,6,FA police officer did not act with
OL,7,F"sensitivity" when he intervened at a
OL,8,FTroubles memorial event during Covid
OL,9,Frestrictions, Police Ombudsman Marie
OL,10,FAnderson has said.
OL,12,FHowever, Mrs Anderson added that she
OL,13,Fbelieved there had been "reasonable
OL,14,Fjustification" for police to have
OL,15,Fattended the scene outside Sean
OL,16,FGraham's bookmakers on the Ormeau Road
OL,17,Fin Belfast in February 2021.
