OL,3,COfficer 'did not act with sensitivity'
OL,4,Cat Sean Graham memorial
OL,6,FA number of people had gathered to
OL,7,Fmark the 29th anniversary of the
OL,8,Fmurders of five people in a loyalist
OL,9,Fgun attack.
OL,11,FThe ombudsman investigated a complaint
OL,12,Ffrom Mark Sykes, a survivor of the
OL,13,Fattack, who was arrested and put into
OL,14,Fhandcuffs before being released after
OL,15,Falmost 90 minutes.
