OL,3,COfficer 'did not act with sensitivity'
OL,4,Cat Sean Graham memorial
OL,6,FThe investigation centred on
OL,7,Fallegations concerning the
OL,8,Finsensitivity of police attending the
OL,9,Farea during the commemoration, Mr
OL,10,FSykes' alleged wrongful arrest and the
OL,11,Fprolonged use of handcuffs.
OL,13,FThe ombudsman said: "Given the
OL,14,Frestrictions on gatherings which were
OL,15,Fin place under the Covid regulations
OL,16,Fat the time, I am satisfied that there
OL,17,Fwas reasonable justification for PSNI
OL,18,Fto have attended the scene.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
