OL,6,FThe PPS directed no prosecution.
OL,8,FThe ombudsman also assessed the
OL,9,Fconduct of seven police officers,
OL,10,Fincluding those who were at the scene,
OL,11,Fin the control room and the senior
OL,12,Fofficers involved in the decision
OL,13,Fmaking.
