OL,6,FMrs Anderson said the evidence had
OL,7,Fbeen sufficient to support her
OL,8,Frecommendations to the PSNI's
OL,9,FProfessional Standards Department
OL,10,F(PSD) for disciplinary proceedings
OL,11,Fregarding one officer's conduct in
OL,12,Frelation to the man's arrest and
OL,13,Fhandcuffing.
OL,15,FThe recommendations were accepted by
OL,16,Fthe PSD and disciplinary proceedings
OL,17,Fwere held.
