OL,6,FHowever, the officer subsequently
OL,7,Fappealed against the decision of the
OL,8,Fdisciplinary panel, and the appeal was
OL,9,Fupheld.
OL,11,FMrs Anderson said radio transmissions
OL,12,Fshowed that when police officers first
OL,13,Fencountered the commemoration they
OL,14,Fthought it was a "pop-up protest" and
OL,15,Fwere not aware of the significance of
OL,16,Fthe gathering.
