OL,6,FThe officers, who were both
OL,7,Fprobationary officers with less than
OL,8,F12 months' service, were given orders
OL,9,Fto establish what was happening and
OL,10,Fwere instructed by their supervising
OL,11,Fsergeant to put their body worn video
OL,12,Fon and to "back off" if they met
OL,13,Fresistance.
OL,15,FTwelve minutes later the attending
OL,16,Fofficers were advised that the
OL,17,Fgathering was to commemorate the
OL,18,Fanniversary of the Sean Graham
OL,19,Fbookmakers shootings.
