OL,6,FThey were told to "still get footage,
OL,7,Fbut treat with sensitivity".
OL,9,FFollowing a verbal altercation, Mr
OL,10,FSykes was arrested for disorderly
OL,11,Fbehaviour and resisting arrest.
OL,13,FHe was placed in a police car where he
OL,14,Fremained with his hands cuffed behind
OL,15,Fhim for almost 90 minutes.
