OL,6,FThe ombudsman said: "The evidence
OL,7,Fdemonstrated that the attending police
OL,8,Fofficers had no advance knowledge of
OL,9,Fthe event or an in-depth understanding
OL,10,Fof the atrocity which was being
OL,11,Fcommemorated."
OL,13,FMrs Anderson said she had identified
OL,14,Fno evidence of a breach of the PSNI
OL,15,Fcode of ethics by senior police
OL,16,Fofficers.
OL,18,FShe has made three recommendations to
OL,19,Fthe PSNI to improve aspects of
OL,20,Foperational policing.
