OL,6,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher said
OL,7,Fthe force accepted the recommendations.
OL,9,FHe said: "We have already commenced
OL,10,Fupdating our training, policy and
OL,11,Fprocedures to ensure that incidents of
OL,12,Fa similar nature do not occur again."
OL,14,FThe ombudsman pointed out that her
OL,15,Finvestigation was distinct from a
OL,16,Fdecision by the PSNI to suspend one
OL,17,Fpolice officer and re-position another.
